<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Untuk Sahabat Gamersku</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #111111;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            border: 3px solid #FFD700; /* Warna Kuning Emas */
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            max-width: 500px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #FFD700;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #FFD700;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .btn-game {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: #FFD700;
            color: #111;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>GGS, WP!</h1>
        <p>Dari Dunia <span class="highlight">Roblox</span> ke Persahabatan Nyata.</p>
        <p>Terima kasih sudah jadi rekan tim yang hebat selama ini!</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn-game">KITA ADALAH TIM</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
